	<h1 class="title">A&amp;F 式的生活方式到底是怎样一种生活方式？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/75588/small/75588.jpg?1431919455" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">张金晶 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-18 13:28:53 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19340/medium/19340.jpg?1450432219" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="19340" data-title="《A&amp;F 式的生活方式到底是怎样一种生活方式？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/19340/medium/19340.jpg?1450432219" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/19340.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
